<title>nǐ shì zhǔ de xiǎo yáng 迦南1273</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì zhǔ de xiǎo yáng zhǔ ài de xiǎo yáng yé sū xún zhǎo nǐ fān guò zuò zuò shān gǎng
 cóng cǐ zhǔ shí shí péi bàn nǐ shēn páng nǐ de rén shēng chōng mǎn le xī wàng
 yé sū zhēn ài nǐ cháng cháng jì xīn shàng yé sū zhēn ài nǐ tiān tiān jì xīn shàng</lyrics>
</song>